===Etymology===
From {{AGr.}} '''[[ονοματοποιία]]''' (''onomatopoiia'') "the coining of a word in imitation of a sound", from '''[[ονοματοποιέω]]''' (''onomatopoieo'') "to coin names", from '''{{polytonic|[[ὄνομα]]}}''' (''onoma'') "name" + '''{{polytonic|[[ποιέω]]}}''' (''poieo'') "to make, to do, to produce".

